room_title: Escape room "Da Vinci's Secret" by Bust Out Escape Room in Albuquerque
review: The Da Vinci puzzles had a lot of variety and were fun to solve. Can't wait to do the other rooms!

room_title: Escape room "Da Vinci's Secret" by Bust Out Escape Room in Albuquerque
review: Took the family to try the new Da Vinci's secret room. We all had a lot of fun and loved the theme. The puzzles were challenging but fun for the whole family. Beat it with a few minutes to spare. We will definitely be going back to try their other rooms. Thanks for making this room, it's a great theme!
